- v0.0.5 regression ratings
- v0.0.6 uncertainty + P(A>B)
- v0.0.7 results.json artifacts
- v0.0.8 config
- v0.0.9 exports
- v0.1.0 stable schema + docs
- Future: adapters (`lm-eval-harness`, `lighteval`), mixed effects, IRT, hosted leaderboard generator

